        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figures 9 - 13. Pampsilota africanus: 9. Valvulae 3 (lateral aspect); 10. Valvulae 3 (dorsal aspect); 11. Lancet; 12. Serrulae 10 - 11; 13. Penis valve (left, lateral aspect)." , "Figures 66 - 71. Pampsilota tsavoensis ♀ (HT), dorsal / lateral. 68 - 71. Pampsilota zebra. 68 - 69 ♀ (HT), dorsal / lateral; 70 - 71. ♂ (PT), dorsal / lateral. Scale bars = 1 mm." , "Figures 38 - 44. Pampsilota afer ♀: 38. Dark form, dorsal; 39 - 40. Pale form, dorsal / lateral. 41 - 44. Pampsilota africanus. 41 - 42. ♀ (LT), dorsal / lateral; 43 - 44. ♂, dorsal / lateral. Scale bars = 1 mm." , "Figures 45 - 50. Pampsilota brandbergensis ♂ (PT), dorsal / lateral. 47 - 50. Pampsilota dahomeyanus. 47 - 48. ♀, dorsal / lateral; 49 - 50. ♂, dorsal / lateral. Scale bars = 1 mm." , "Figures 60 - 65. Pampsilota leleupi ♂ (HT), dorsal / lateral. 62 - 63. Pampsilota luederitzensis ♂ (PT), dorsal / lateral. 64 - 65. Pampsilota nigeriae ♂ (HT), dorsal / lateral. Scale bars = 1 mm." , "Figures 1 - 3. Pampsilota sp.: 1. Antenna; 2. tarsal claw; 3. Fore wing (above), hind wing (below)." , "Figures 31 - 35. Pampsilota zebra: 31. Valvulae 3 (lateral aspect); 32. Valvulae 3 (dorsal aspect); 33. Lancet; 34. Serrulae 9 - 11; 35. Penis valve (left, lateral aspect)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/118809" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/118803" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/118817" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/118811" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/118789" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/118791" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/118815" .

